About the Author

Adya is a passionate student with a keen interest in all subjects, and a recent affinity to neuroscience. With a background in STEM fields and competitions, Adya enjoys exploring the complexities of various complicated topics, wondering about technologies such as time travel, the human mind, and the ethical dilemmas that arise from scientific advancements. When not writing, she can be found delving into coding projects, solving puzzles, studying, playing sports, spending time with her wonderful family, and enjoying the latest trends in music and chess! 

She aspires to continue creating content that everyone can enjoy and looks forward to accompanying you on another wonderful and thrilling reading adventure! 
